===Speak with Esther{{subst:void|<!--300030101-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=daily|location=Master Control Zone|Researcher Esther is having a rough day with her appearance. She wants to change her hair color, but she doesn't know what colors to change to. With your unique perspective on beauty, go and advise Esther!}}
{{Dialogue Start}}

;(Talk to Esther)
:'''Esther:''' I'm catching up with some old girlfriends in a few days. It's been years since we last met up. I wonder... would they laugh at me for being out of touch with fashion?
:'''Esther:''' I've heard of you from Lead Researcher Asta. You seem to know a lot, and might have your own insights on fashion.
:'''Esther:''' Can I ask for your advice? ...Do you think I should dye my hair a different color?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} The current color is fine.
::'''Esther:''' But I think it feels a little old-fashioned.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What color would you like?
::'''Esther:''' *sigh* I can't really decide...
:'''Esther:''' Fashion is changing every day... I've had white hair for so long that it's about time for a change.
:'''Esther:''' Apparently, the most fashionable colors these days are blue and brown, but both colors have their pros and cons. It's so hard to choose.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why have to choose?
::'''Esther:''' I do want to try them both, but the quality of my hair won't allow me to experiment too much.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Blue! I like blue!
::'''Esther:''' Blue makes people think about the sea, the sky, and the universe... Wait! I'm not asking which color you like. I want to know which hair color looks better!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Brown! I like brown!
::'''Esther:''' Brown has a warm feeling to it... Wait! I'm not asking which color you like. I want to know which hair color looks better!
:'''Esther:''' I heard some researchers have already dyed their hair these colors. I'd love to see them for myself.
:'''Esther:''' But my work at the Department of Insight is not done. I really can't leave yet... So, could I please ask you to take some photos for me?
:'''Esther:''' I want to see what these colors look like under the space station's lights, and which color would suit me better... Hmm, could you please lend a hand?
{{Dialogue End}}

