:'''(Trailblazer):''' (I'm done with Esther's photos. Time to take these back to her.)

;(Talk to Esther)
:'''Esther:''' Ohhh, lemme see... This looks good. But I have an issue.
:'''Esther:''' Look, the lights in the space station make blue look rigid, and make brown look dull.
:'''Esther:''' What should I do? Maybe neither color looks good? (Trailblazer), you're young and fashionable. Help me pick the color that suits me.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Blue!
::'''Esther:''' Okay, blue it is. It's not bad. It gives a feeling of vastness and open space.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Brown!
::'''Esther:''' Mmm, you can't go wrong with brown.
:'''Esther:''' Young people do think fast. I'll defer to you on this! Thank you. You can try a different hair color yourself, you know.
